@__mutex The policy's we have in place are used to ensure our customer's accounts are secure, as this is always our priority. I understand you are dissatisfied. Please reach out via DM to discuss further.

@__mutex Please reach out via DM if you would like to escalate a complaint regarding this. A case manager will be in touch with you within 5 business days to assess and see if another option is available for you.

@__mutex Securing your accounts is our top priority. That's why we provide a range of security features and services, including fraud prevention technology and secure banking, to help you stay safe. If you are dissatisfied with the policy, please capture a complaint via the link.

@__mutex Hi, I understand that you have previously been referred to the branch. If our phone team is unable to verify you, please visit the branch so that we can assist. If you are dissatisfied with our ID policy, please capture a complaint via our website: https://t.co/4qtaZUyHbV ^Chris
